procstep.procdesc: Excel Spreadsheet provided by Lt. Bruton of SFPD listed private school addresses. This set of records was geocoded against City Lots layer. Remaining unmatched records were researched and assigned location.

Dataset updated using National Center for Education Statistics PSS Private School Universe Survey data 2007-2008 school year. Dowloaded from http://nces.ed.gov/surveys/pss. PSS dataset and Excel Spreadsheet provided by Lt. Bruton of SFPD were crossreferenced to find differences. Unmatched records were researched and updated.
